  <summary date="2021-08-24T17:20:25Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Human Trafficking and Exploitation Prevention Training Act of 2020

This bill establishes a demonstration grant program within the Administration for Children and Families for nonprofits, local and state education agencies, and elementary and secondary schools to train students, school personnel, and parents to recognize and prevent human trafficking and child exploitation.</summary>
